<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Assuming, though, that he still owns 73.1 mill=
ion shares of Twitter, and that he does not want to sell those shares befor=
e a court decides if the deal is off or not, then=C2=A0those shares are an =
interesting bargaining chip for a settlement. Musk paid=C2=A0<a href=3D"htt=
ps://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28351521.280590/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cu=
c2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzE0MTgwOTEvMDAwMTEwNDY1OTIyMDQyODYzL3R=
tMjIxMTc1N2QxX3NjMTNkLmh0bQ/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBb334198e/email" itempr=
